OL,3,CGerman side deny allegation of racist
OL,4,Cabuse against Liverpool
OL,6,FA German team accused of racism which
OL,7,Fcaused players and coaches to walk off
OL,8,Fthe pitch during a youth match has
OL,9,Frejected the allegations against it.
OL,11,FLiverpool FC said one of its under 18
OL,12,Fplayers reported being racially abused
OL,13,Fby a member of Hoffenheim during the
OL,14,Fmatch on 19 July.
OL,16,FThe player was abused again in a game
OL,17,Fat the same event against Eintracht
OL,18,FFrankfurt the following day.
