OL,3,CGerman side deny allegation of racist
OL,4,Cabuse against Liverpool
OL,6,FHowever Bundesliga club Hoffenheim
OL,7,Fbelieve Liverpool misheard a German
OL,8,Fslang work used by the team and have
OL,9,Fsaid "there is definitely no racism
OL,10,Famong the TSG players".
OL,12,FHoffenheim said they took the
OL,13,Faccusation very seriously but "firmly
OL,14,Freject its content".
OL,16,FA club statement read: "There is no
OL,17,Fracist discrimination in the TSG
OL,18,F(Hoffenheim) academy and never has
OL,19,Fbeen in the past.
