OL,3,CGerman side deny allegation of racist
OL,4,Cabuse against Liverpool
OL,6,F"We have many players of different
OL,7,Fethnicities in our youth academy who
OL,8,Fcompete with each other in sport.
OL,10,F"Differences of opinion can occur here
OL,11,Fand there, but there is definitely no
OL,12,Fracism among the TSG players.
OL,14,F"The accused player and surrounding
OL,15,Fteam-mates have told us that the
OL,16,Falleged statement was not made. The
OL,17,Fanalysis of our video recording also
OL,18,Frevealed nothing.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
