OL,3,CGerman side deny allegation of racist
OL,4,Cabuse against Liverpool
OL,6,F"Nevertheless, we are carefully
OL,7,Fworking through the incident with our
OL,8,Fteam of psychologists and the child
OL,9,Fprotection officer.
OL,11,F"One possible explanation for the
OL,12,Forigin of this accusation and the fact
OL,13,Fthat it was repeated against Frankfurt
OL,14,Fcould be the fact that the German
OL,15,Fslang word 'Digga' (roughly equivalent
OL,16,Fto 'Bro' in English) has a phonetic
OL,17,Fsimilarity to the swear word allegedly
OL,18,Fused."
OL,20,FHoffenheim said they would not name
OL,21,Fthe accused player.
