OL,6,FA club statement issued on Saturday
OL,7,Fread: "Liverpool FC can confirm that a
OL,8,Fmember of our under-18s team reported
OL,9,Fhe was racially abused by an opponent
OL,10,Fwhile playing in the Bundesliga Cup
OL,11,Fyouth tournament at Schwabisch Hall in
OL,12,FGermany on Friday.
OL,14,F"The player immediately alerted the
OL,15,Fmatch official, his team-mates, and
OL,16,Four coaching staff.
OL,18,F"Consequently, LFC's management team
OL,19,Fdecided to stop the game and leave the
OL,20,Fpitch together.
OL,26,@oD@GOUvD@AOU
