OL,3,CGerman side deny allegation of racist
OL,4,Cabuse against Liverpool
OL,6,F"In a further incident, the same
OL,7,Fplayer was the target of abuse during
OL,8,Fa fixture in the tournament today.
OL,9,FAgain, the player alerted his team-
OL,10,Fmates and coaching staff and our
OL,11,Fmanagement team opted to leave the
OL,12,Fpitch once more.
OL,14,F"We are proud of our player for his
OL,15,Fprompt actions in reporting the
OL,16,Fincident and the maturity of his
OL,17,Fresponse.
OL,19,F"He and any of his team-mates affected
OL,20,Fare being supported by the Academy
OL,21,Fsafeguarding team.
